Titolo: NHL 2K3

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: NHL 2K3 is a hockey video game developed for the GameCube, PlayStation 2, and Xbox by Treyarch and published by Sega. It features Jeremy Roenick on the cover. It is the only game in the NHL 2K series to be released on the GameCube.
NHL 2K3 utilizes ESPN's presentation and was the first hockey game developed to utilize the Xbox Live and the PS2 Online online service. The rosters are from the 2002â€“2003 NHL season.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: 89
